title: Anna Faris is Unqualified
description:
Anna Faris (pronounced Ahhhna) calls herself unqualified but it’s not a bit. This week Ashley and Claire dive into her book on life and love to discover how truly, deeply unqualified she is to be giving any sort of relationship advice at all. 


Download June's Journey FREE today on the Apple App Store or Google Play.


Come see our live Moment House show from anywhere! Tickets at https://www.momenthouse.com/cmbc


Join the Patreon for new episodes every Thursday! https://www.patreon.com/celebritymemoirbookclub

Our next comedy show at Nicky’s Unisex is Thursday, March 10 at 7 pm!!

Follow us on Twitter @cmbc_podcast and Instagram @celebritymemoirbookclub 


Art by @adrianne_manpearl and theme song by @ashleesimpsonross
